Common.Highlight.Common.Text: Minutes from the M5 on / off ramps

Common.LongDescription.Common.Text:
350 Edgar Street offers a highly functional warehouse within a desirable actively managed estate. The unit benefits from B-Double access, ample car parking and ability to set down containers, in conjunction with a well-presented office. 

Strategically located, this secure facility also provides excellent access to the M5 Motorway via the River Road.

Key Features include:
- 1,219sqm*
- Up to 8m* clearance
- B-Double access
- Ability to set down containers
- 200 amps of power
- Generous parking allocation
- Minutes from the M5 via River Road (on & off ramps)
- IN1 - General Industrial

For more information please contact the exclusively listed agents of CBRE & LJHC Bankstown.

CBRE is pleased to offer a newly refurbished 76 Harley Crescent, Condell Park for lease.

76 Harley Crescent is a freestanding high-quality office and warehouse facility that has just undergone a comprehensive refurbishment. The clear span warehouse also features a small air-conditioned mezzanine which could be utilised as a clean room or packing area. The open-plan office/showroom area presents well with existing boardrooms, training rooms and facilities.

The property is well-positioned close to the M5 Motorway and is only moments from Bankstown Airport and & Moorebank Intermodal. 

Property Highlights:
-Total Building area: 2,499-2,899sqm*
- Site area: 4,327sqm*
- Up to 8.5m* internal clearance 
- Zoning – IN2 Light Industrial 
- Regular shaped clear span warehouse
- Easy access to M5 Motorway
- Drive through awning
- Well presented office and showroom

For more information please contact the exclusive agents.

CBRE and M5 Industrial are pleased to present Warehouse A/87 Allingham Street, Condell Park to market for lease. The property is ideally positioned in the heart of the Inner South West and within close proximity to Henry Lawson Drive, M5 Motorway and is only moment from Moorebank Intermodal and Bankstown Airport. 

Property Highlights:
 - Asking Rent: $100psm net 
- Warehouse: 2,732SQM* - 2,982SQM* 
- Up to 8.5m* internal clearance
 - Zoning IN2 – Light Industrial 
 - Regular shape warehouses
 - Outgoings: $15/sqm

For more information please contact the exclusive agents at CBRE or M5 Industrial.
